<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />
    <title>Climate Solutions</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar', {page: '/home'}) %>
    <main>
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <div class="hero bg-base-200 h-[500px]">
        <div class="hero-content text-center">
          <div class="max-w-lg">
            <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold">Explore Our Projects üåç</h1>
            <p class="py-6">
              Dive into innovative climate solutions driving real change. From
              renewable energy initiatives to sustainable practices, our
              projects are shaping a greener, brighter future. Discover how
              we're making a difference‚Äîand how you can be part of it!
            </p>
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/solutions/projects"
              >See Projects</a
            >
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="container mx-auto">
        <!-- Projects Section -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5 my-10">
          <div class="card px-5 bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
            <figure>
              <img
                class="w-full"
                src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions/solution_farmlandrestoration01.jpg"
                alt="Shoes"
              />
            </figure>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h2 class="card-title">Abandoned Farmland Restoration</h2>
              <p>
                Restoration can bring degraded farmland back into productivity
                and sequester carbon in the process.
              </p>
              <div class="card-actions justify-center">
                <a href="/solutions/projects/1" class="btn btn-primary"
                  >See More</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card px-5 bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
            <figure>
              <img
                class="w-full"
                src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions2020/solution_alternativecement02.jpg"
                alt="Shoes"
              />
            </figure>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h2 class="card-title">Alternative Cement</h2>
              <p>
                Conventional cement production is a significant source of carbon
                dioxide. Reformulation can reduce emissions by millions of
                metric tons each year.
              </p>
              <div class="card-actions justify-center">
                <a href="/solutions/projects/2" class="btn btn-primary"
                  >See More</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="card px-5 bg-base-100 shadow-xl">
            <figure>
              <img
                class="w-full"
                src="https://drawdown.org/sites/default/files/solutions2020/solution_bicycle_infrastructure.jpg"
                alt="Shoes"
              />
            </figure>
            <div class="card-body">
              <h2 class="card-title">Bicycle Infrastructure</h2>
              <p>
                Infrastructure is essential for supporting safe and abundant
                bicycle use, which curbs emissions by reducing the need for
                fossil-fuel-dependent transportation.
              </p>
              <div class="card-actions justify-center">
                <a href="/solutions/projects/3" class="btn btn-primary"
                  >See More</a
                >
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
